sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Kiosk
    participant Order
    participant Payment as PaymentStrategy
    participant APCard as APCardPayment
    participant QR as QRCodePayment
    participant Logger as TransactionLogger

    Note over Kiosk,QR: Strategy pattern lets the kiosk use interchangeable payment methods.
    User->>Kiosk: confirmOrder()
    Kiosk->>Order: calculateTotal()
    Order-->>Kiosk: amount
    alt AP card selected
        Kiosk->>APCard: pay(amount)
        APCard-->>Kiosk: approved / declined
    else future QR selected
        Kiosk->>QR: generateQR()
        QR-->>User: QR token
        Kiosk->>Payment: pay(amount)
        Payment-->>Kiosk: approved / declined
    end
    alt payment approved
        Kiosk->>Order: markPaid()
        Kiosk->>Order: submit()
        Note over Logger: Singleton pattern provides one shared transaction log.
        Kiosk->>Logger: getInstance().log(kioskId, order)
        Logger-->>Kiosk: logged
    else payment declined
        Kiosk-->>User: displayPaymentError()
    end
